# SEO URL migration → hyphenated slugs (301, must come BEFORE the catch-all).
# The old concatenated slugs no longer have a static shell dir, so these
# permanent redirects apply and preserve link equity to the new landing pages.
/calendariomundial2026   /calendario-mundial-2026   301
/worldcup2026calendar    /world-cup-2026-calendar    301

# SPA fallback so React Router can handle deep-links client-side.
# Note: Render Static Sites silently ignores external URLs in _redirects
# (neither 200! nor 3xx work). Share-preview routes /c/* and /p/* are
# served directly by api.futpools.com — see APIClient.swift / share helpers.
/p/*    /index.html   200
/c/*    /index.html   200
/*      /index.html   200
